Text: "my travelling journey start from 2016, when i am challenging my self to travel\
  \ around south east asia for 5 country in 2 weeks. start from singapore, malaysia,\
  \ thailand, cambodia, and vietnam. \ni wanna beat myself for all the things.. one\
  \ of the most valuable when i'm going for this travel is i get what i never expect\
  \ before.  for the experience, the people, the place, culture and many things..\
  \ that build me to the strong woman, brave, and make me more mature, start from\
  \ there now i really want to travel around the world to get a lot of unexpected\
  \ experinnce. it' s not only good experince but bad also and i really enjoy it.\
  \ for this travel i really love to share about cambodia, the biggest temple for\
  \ 7 magical in the world.. this is ankor wat and i really amaze with the beauty\
  \ of this place. i wish i can see the beauty of god creation and get amazing experience.\
  \ after travellinh my life change, i change to be a independent woman who can decide\
  \ the most things in my life, really love to meet new people and interact with them,\
  \ and i really like to leaen about new culture. that's all my travelling experience..\
  \ thank you"
